This paper deals with content-aware image retargeting, which is a computer vision problem related to image processing and computer graphics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), and the use of image attributes, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics). Additionally, the paper discusses the human perception of image retargeting, which could relate to cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and the use of image search engines, which could relate to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
